'''Disney Junior Israel''' is a Digital Israeli language television station for young children and their parents owned by [[The Walt Disney Company]]. That Channel Brands in [[July 18]], [[2011]] on [[Yes (Israel)|YES]] and later It will be in [[HOT (Israel)|Hot]].<ref>[http://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-4096373,00.html]</ref> ==Shows== === Series === * [[Handy Manny]] * [[Jungle Junction]] * [[Mickey Mouse Clubhouse]] * [[Special Agent Oso]] * [[Art Attack]] * [[Jake and the Never Land Pirates]]
